{
  "text": "We reported earlier on packaging DFB diode lasers self-injection locked by means of electro-optically active WGM resonators into small form factor with 44\u00d727\u00d714 mm dimensions. We used lithium tantalate as the resonator host material and applied voltage to the resonator to tune the laser frequency. [CITATION_1] In this work we report on demonstration of efficient optical phase locking of two electro-optically tunable self-injection locked lasers.",
  "citation_candidates": [
